The parasitic '''dead tree''' is an unused scenery object that appears to be a dead tree with a red vine tangled around it. The red vine is described as a parasitic plant, and has a similar appearance to several other unused red vine objects found in the game cache. The parasitic vines may have been intended for use in Karamja or other tropical areas.
